      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Abu Nasr, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Al-Hassan Al-Reza<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The perfume is from the etiquettes of the Prophets<sup>as</sup>’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn abu Nasr who has said the following: “Abu al-Hassan, al-Rida’, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Using perfume is of the moral discipline of the Prophets/” "
        ]
      }
